    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305520/extras/Shoppic1.png?t=1750819651\" /></span><br><br><strong><i>在日本著名的山路上漂移！驾驶各种日本汽车！挑战当地车队！在日本漫画游戏画面风格中！</i></strong><br><br>漂移计划是一个赛车游戏，让你驾驶传奇的JDM汽车，在日本的山路上漂移。用高的漂移技巧打败对手，更新记录，解锁新车！<br>激情的欧洲节拍音乐让你踩下油门！日本漫画风格的游戏画面带回激情时代！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305520/extras/cacb3c01800df5e75d3cd3223506c6fe.avif?t=1750819651\" width=154 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305520/extras/cacb3c01800df5e75d3cd3223506c6fe.avif?t=1750819651\" width=154 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305520/extras/cacb3c01800df5e75d3cd3223506c6fe.avif?t=1750819651\" width=154 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305520/extras/cacb3c01800df5e75d3cd3223506c6fe.avif?t=1750819651\" width=154 height=77 /></span><br><br><strong><i>在本游戏中，您将看到：</i></strong><br><br>■6辆日本名车！<br>■5条不同的山路！<br>■上瘾的漂移系统！<br>■真实的物理悬挂！<br>■日本漫画风格的图形！<br>■完全支持控制器！<br>■精致车辆模型！<br>■可更换的汽车颜色。<br>■惊人的旁观者游戏回放系统！正如你在视频中看到的。<br>■欧洲节拍音乐！<br><strong>值得关注的新功能</strong><br>■在赛道上放置任意数量种类的AI车辆进行比赛的演习模式！<br>■定制BGM！选择本地mp3文件作为背景音乐，漂移喜欢的旋律<br>■11个蒸汽成就",
